Changes:
 ros-one-compressed-image-transport (1.15.0-9-gcae592c-2024.10.14.22.08) jammy; urgency=high
 .
   * Update maintainer in ros1 branches (#132 <https://github.com/ros-perception/image_transport_plugins/issues/132>)
