   * Add a basic loopback unit test (#61 <https://github.com/ros-perception/image_transport_plugins/issues/61>)
   * Contributors: Johannes Meyer, Kenji Brameld, Lucas Walter, Max Schwarz, Michael Carroll, ijnek, v4hn
